#

Borscht with Sauerkraut

60 min
$12.5
220 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodHealthy

Description

A vibrant beetroot soup enriched with tangy sauerkraut for a delightful flavor twist.

Ingredients

  • beets: 4 medium
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • potatoes: 2 medium, diced
  • carrots: 1 large, diced
  • onion: 1 large, chopped
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • sauerkraut: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • dill: for garnish
